title: Seafood Fettuccine
ingredients: ["6 oz. fettuccine", "1/4 c. butter", "2 cloves garlic, finely chopped", "1 (8 oz.) pkg. Louis Kemp Crab Delights flakes or chunks", "1 c. half and half", "1/8 tsp. black pepper", "1/2 c. Parmesan cheese, grated"]
directions: ["Cook fettuccine according to package directions; drain.", "Heat butter and garlic in skillet on medium heat until garlic is lightly browned.", "Add Crab Delights, half and half and pepper.", "Heat about 3 minutes or until mixture just begins to bubble, stirring occasionally.", "Add Parmesan cheese; stir for 1 minute.", "Remove from heat.", "Toss Crab Delight sauce with fettuccine.", "Serve immediately with additional Parmesan cheese, if desired.", "Makes four 1-cup servings."]
